com.planetj.taste.impl.correlation
Class CosineMeasureCorrelation

java.lang.Object
  com.planetj.taste.impl.correlation.CosineMeasureCorrelation
All Implemented Interfaces:
Refreshable, ItemCorrelation, UserCorrelation
public final class CosineMeasureCorrelation
extends java.lang.Object

An implementation of the cosine measure itemCorrelation. Each User X and Y is treated as a vector of preferences. Their itemCorrelation is given as the dot product of the vectors divided by the product of their magnitudes, which can be interpreted as the cosine of the angle between the vectors.

Author:
Sean Owen
